&lt;b&gt;What steps will reproduce the problem?&lt;/b&gt;
I instrumented tests/pepper_plugin/plugin_object.cc to request a 
reinitialization of the 3d context once per second.

What is the expected output?
Once per second you might see a flash as the 3d context is deleted and 
recreated.

What do you see instead?
Once per second, the 3d context window disappears.

Note: Placing the mouse over the 3d area (with or without moving the mouse) 
results in the correct expected behavior.




